                                                                                                         You are free to:
                                                                                             - Use this software for personal, educational, or commercial purposes.
                                                                                             - Modify, fork, and create derivative works based on this software.

                                                                                                    2. Attribution Requirement
                                                                                         -  You must give clear and visible credit to the original author ("Ryan") in any redistributed or derivative work.
                                                                                        - You may not claim to be the original creator of this project or its codebase.

                                                                                                3. Design Documents and Add-ons
                                                                                       - You may not claim ownership of the original design documents or game design concepts.
                                                                                       - You may include the original design documents as part of your own project, but only as supplemental or reference material, clearly labeled as part of the                                                                                             original work.

                                                                                                4. Redistribution
                                                                                       - If you distribute modified versions or derivative works, include a notice stating that changes were made and a link to the original project if available.
                                                                                        - This license must be included with any distribution.

                                                                                                5. No Warranty
                                                                                     This software is provided “as is”, without warranty of any kind. The author is not liable for any damages resulting from its use.

